CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1960, pg. A3, reads: " "Y-Phalanx Award Winners - The fourth annual banquet of the Y-Phalanx Fraternity was held on March 27 at the Centre Avenue YMCA. Following the etsablished [sic] custom, awards were given to members for outstanding services performed...On the right, Vice Primas Leroy Lowry presents a trophy to Russell Washington for outstanding work with the YMCA and the fraternity.  Mr. Washington is adviser to the Y-Phalanx Fraternity.-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Leroy Lowry presenting trophy to Russell Washington for outstanding work with YMCA and Y-Phalanx, during Y-Phalanx Fraternity banquet, Centre Avenue YMCA
